| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6033 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5e27382d-d48a-5e9a-92ee-9d9cdbe57779"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
